metadata.name: Slow and Steady
metadata.description:
With Nocturne, I explore the wonders and terrors I encounter deep into the night. To experience the silences, the songs, and the surreal hidden away and to be able to capture its essence has been an enlightening experience for me.

"Slow and Steady"
Nocturne by Waytoomad

Photographed in Burbank, California
Photographed dimensions: 5000 × 4000 px
